data.current_description: Watches all creatives pertaining to a bidder. It is sufficient to invoke this endpoint once per bidder. A Pub/Sub topic will be created and notifications will be pushed to the topic when any of the bidder's creatives change status. All of the bidder's service accounts will have access to read from the topic. Subsequent invocations of this method will return the existing Pub/Sub configuration.
data.summary_suggestion: Watch bidder creatives for status changes
data.description_suggestion: Establishes a watch on all creatives for a bidder account, enabling real-time notifications via Google Cloud Pub/Sub. When invoked, a Pub/Sub topic is created and configured to receive notifications whenever any of the bidder's creatives change status. All service accounts associated with the bidder have read access to the topic. This operation is idempotent - subsequent invocations return the existing Pub/Sub configuration without creating duplicates. Requires the bidder resource name. Returns the WatchCreativesResponse containing the Pub/Sub topic configuration.
